{"tid":1781452,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【路透社號外】因中國政府施壓，金融新聞情報網Refinitiv封鎖200多宗路透社有關香港示威報道","createTime":"2019-12-13T07:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T16:36:01.000Z","uid":131691,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"39a360165b56fd7a222f15b37748846667e5b243","tid":1781452,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:16:20.000Z","msg":"好大單嘢，請大家入去慢慢睇。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/investigates/special-report/hongkong-protests-media/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Finvestigates%2Fspecial-report%2Fhongkong-protests-media%2F&d=ZRuO0gn2PDb4CPS%2BM%2Fpj6kcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=3b394d75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Finvestigates%2Fspecial-report%2Fhongkong-protests-media%2F&h=607446b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/investigates/special-report/hongkong-protests-media/</a><br />\n以下係節錄，但係真係請大家入內文讀，因爲太多細節：<br />\nRefinitiv曾經屬於路透社同一間母公司，Thomson Reuters<br />\n而家Refinitiv獨立出嚟，但係依然係路透社一個好大嘅經濟夥伴，尤其負責Eikon呢個金融情報網絡，散播資料，當中好多都係路透社嘅新聞<br />\n今年夏天，Refinitiv安裝咗一個過濾系統<br />\n事後，好多新聞都離奇消失，包括路透社報道香港信貸評級下降嘅資料，喺中國睇Eikon會被完全封鎖<br />\n<br />\n想知道突別有關香港嘅，可以scroll落 &quot;Restricted News&quot; 嗰個section，但係其中兩單突別顯眼：<br />\n7月尾，路透社報道有中國官員喺香港鼓勵市民驅趕示威者，Refinitiv要求路透社review篇報道，點知下個禮拜就出現黃藍市民互打嘅情況。中國官員插手香港呢篇新聞被Refinitiv封鎖。<br />\n8月30號後，Refinitiv嘅新聞封鎖轉強，30號之前只有5單路透社有關香港嘅新聞被封鎖；<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8月30號後至到11月20號，每5篇就有4篇被封鎖。</span></span><br />\n9月4號至10月7號，所有路透社有關香港嘅報道都被封鎖。當時一切塑膠子彈及水炮車嘅新聞，都被Refinitiv封鎖。"},{"pid":"9b80a368af78c78b5b8025ac6170354d054f421e","tid":1781452,"uid":60334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T07:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de583fc2547